Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磅蛋糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 要是您知道能做好吃的訣竅 能不能告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想啊 最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這是我們的食譜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我調整成在家裏也可以做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先照這個試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我能做出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 做點心就像是數學一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要正確計算材料 遵守合理的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定會出現同樣的回答 做出同樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試想著吃它的人的表情來做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼怎麼 你要烤蛋糕？好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我想明天登山的時候帶去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵竟然是戶外系啊 真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟男朋友一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不是的 只有女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 葵明明很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我會買禮物回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 我太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備這樣就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想著吃它的人的表情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 就算是日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是用那種表情來吃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能會有點開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要努力做出愛意滿滿的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 明天要和日向去登約定的大山 谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓和心夏也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.27,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(534,412)}心夏的飯能大冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}致心夏 雖然早了一天 生日快樂！今晚一起慶祝吧 by媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣和替換衣服 水 點心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再拿一條毛巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過想要 媽媽記得呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合適
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要登一下天覽山嗎 還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子也說請用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:07:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少年沒來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的像是身處童話世界一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏的話 就算有妖精也不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽好慢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉哦 來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:10:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明天要去谷川岳吧 所以打算今天給你慶祝的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕店也關門了 只能買便利店的蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呢 禮物我準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我準備行李的時候發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是太大意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常開心哦 謝謝 尺寸也非常合適
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不由得就走到了兒童森林公園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了那麼遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然有點熱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風非常舒服 景色也很美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還讀了懷念的書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夕陽映射的葉子閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美美的 很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且媽媽也為了我急忙趕回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天我非常開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛意滿滿的蛋糕終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕快睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天我們倆要再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 約定實現了會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登上谷川岳 再下去 那之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未完待續
